title: Bill Belichick Needs To Rename His Boat ‘VI Rings’ After Super Bowl LI Win | NESN Sports Today | NESN.com
text:
by NESN Video on Mon, Feb 6, 2017 at 11:44PM 1,482 Tweet 
Tom Brady and Bill Belichick are the most successful quarterback/head coach combo in NFL history. 
The two New England Patriots legends led their team to victory in thrilling fashion Sunday night with a 34-28 overtime win against the Atlanta Falcons in Super Bowl LI. 
Will the Patriots repeat as champions next season? Check out what Jermaine Wiggins thinks in the “NESN Sports Today” video above, presented by People’s United Bank.
